data.description: Great investment opportunity with a tenant occupied home in a beautiful gated master planned community. This practically new, immaculate 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is nestled in the Craig Ranch master planned community. The gourmet kitchen, which features upgraded cabinets and quartz countertops, is the centerpiece of the open concept floor plan and the layout...the layout is perfect for family gatherings and dinner parties. All bedrooms are upstairs, but there is separation so everyone has their privacy. The backyard is fully fenced and you are steps away from the community park and picnic area.
